{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":578914,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":120578,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"那个学弟怎么办呢，分析的头头是道，最重要的公平还是没有","timestamp":1605782794,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":578926,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":120578,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"假设无监控带来的反转，学弟的未来四年要怎么过呢\n\n人比热度更值得关心吧","timestamp":1605782883,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":578953,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":120578,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"qs","timestamp":1605783006,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":578966,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":120578,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"后者，坏人无法被谴责有的也会心不安，但好人被诬陷真的想死一样","timestamp":1605783102,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":578973,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":120578,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"所以你想说的是，学姐也不应该说出来，或许一开始这个监控没有出来就是最好的，达到了一个最小化的情况，您这种圣人角度可真是奇特","timestamp":1605783111,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":579014,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":120578,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"她给不给出真实身份是由不得她的。。。","timestamp":1605783487,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":1,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":120578,"reply":6,"tag":null,"text":"#120570\n这倒给我一个奇怪的思路\n从网络暴力的角度讲\n假设无反转 学弟的热度应该会很快消散\n因为性骚扰是一件板上钉钉无法洗也没有人会洗的事\n也就不会有大面积的混战\n但目前的状况确实是倘若学姐给出真实身份 会承受比学弟严重的多的网暴\n因为她拿枪指着好人\n那么\n人们会更害怕做坏人被谴责\n还是害怕做好人被枪指着呢","timestamp":1605782704,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782654,"url":"","vote":{}}}